Implementation Steps:
1. Download the official PlayfairDisplay-Regular.ttf from Google Fonts
2. Place the file at this exact path: src/ios/ios/Fonts/PlayfairDisplay-Regular.ttf
3. Register in Info.plist:
   <key>UIAppFonts</key>
   <array>
       <string>PlayfairDisplay-Regular.ttf</string>
   </array>

